title: Dinner Rolls
description: A delicious, fluffy dinner roll is magical — it can turn even the simplest meal into a memorable experience. This straightforward recipe yields tender, buttery dinner rolls with a soft and squishy interior that begs to be torn apart and savored. Whether served warm with a generous slather of creamy butter or used to mop up the last remnants of a hearty stew, these rolls are versatile companions to any dish or meal. Are you new to bread baking? Don't fret. These rolls are made with easy-to-follow steps and use basic pantry ingredients like milk, water, butter, eggs, and flour. 
